contentrichtext.text: '''Ian Temby''' [[Order of Australia|AO]] [[Queen's Counsel|QC]] (born 1942). First Commissioner of the [[Independent Commission Against Corruption of New South Wales|New South Wales Independent Commission Against Corruption]] (ICAC). More recently commissioner in the Temby Royal Commission into the Finance Broking Industry (report tabled in 2002).
